  "description": [
    "Miss Newport Pageant Open To WAVES Newportbased WAVES single and between the ages of 18 and 28 have been invited by the New port County Junior Chamber of Commerce to become entrants in its Miss Newport pageant The young lady chosen by the Newport County JayCees as Miss Newport will represent the city in the Miss Rhode Island pageant In turn Miss Rhode Island will represent the state in th Miss America pageant Among the rules and regula tions regarding entry in the Miss Newport pageant are the require ments that each entrant must be a high school graduate that her age on 1 Sept shall not be less than 18 nor more than 28 years and that she must be single and never have been married di vorced or had her marriage an nulled Talent Each entrant will be required to display a threeminute routine talent performance This talent may be singing dancing playing a musical instrument dramatic reading art display dress design ing or she may give a three minute talk on the career sh wishes to pursue Complete information regard ing the Miss Newport pageant and rules and regulations govern ing entry is available by calling JayCee"
  ],
